@NODE "Install"

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Installing is easy! Just drag the CyberLemmings drawer to the
    destination where you want it installed. If you want it installed in
    WBStartup, just copy the CyberLemmings executable + icon and gfx
    directory to your WBStartup drawer.

    The MorphOS compiled version is included in the archive also, choose
    the one you prefer :).

@ENDNODE

